@startuml
title Alarm Clock State Machine

[*] --> Off

state "Off" as Off
state "Alarm Set" as AlarmSet
state "Alarm Ringing" as AlarmRinging

Off : entry/Initial state
Off : do/Wait for alarm set

AlarmSet : entry/Alarm set
AlarmSet : do/Wait for alarm time
AlarmSet : exit/Alarm activated

AlarmRinging : entry/Alarm ringing
AlarmRinging : do/Ring the alarm
AlarmRinging : exit/Alarm stopped

Off --> AlarmSet : set alarm
AlarmSet --> AlarmRinging : alarm time reached
AlarmRinging --> AlarmSet : stop alarm
AlarmRinging --> Off : alarm stopped

Off --> [*] : exit

@enduml
